    {
      "id": "settings-switch-to-ai-providers",
      "name": "Switch to AI Providers section",
      "description": "Behavioral: clicking the AI Providers section button navigates from /settings/account to /settings/ai (router.push) — the Account-only 'Signed in as' subheading unmounts. Read-only navigation between settings sections; no preferences are written. The vanish of the Account anchor is the behavioral assertion. activateStates is intentionally empty: the destination is a route change whose section-nav button ids reindex on re-render (the indexed button ordinals shift when the account pane unmounts), so no pre-snapshot structural state is a stable post-condition; the vanish proves the transition took effect.",
      "fromStates": ["settings-section-tabs"],
